Con Murphy’s goal is to achieve the Irish pub experience, while integrating American cuisine combined with great drinks & atmosphere to make all guests feel welcome.
Irish pubs are known all over the world as sanctuaries for a relaxed atmosphere and great sociability.
People often frequent them so they may join in good company and great conversation with old friends, new friends and staff members who always make them feel welcome.
Our staff members play an important role in recreating the Irish pub experience by extending a natural hospitality for all of our guests.
There are no strangers at Con Murphy’s, only friends we have not met.
